convertUInt32ToFloat¶

zserio.float.convertUInt32ToFloat(float32Value: int) → float[source]¶

Converts 32-bit float stored as an integer value to python native float.

Parameters

float32Value – Single precision float value stored as an integer value to convert.

Returns

Converted python native float.
